overview: March 1st, 2008 :: The second annual King of Trios tournament rages on, with action featuring Team WWF, los Luchadores de Mexico, Canada's Team IWS, and a breakout performance by Da Soul Touchaz! Two elimination rounds whittle down 14 trios, by night's end, just 4 trios advance.
title: Chikara King Of Trios 2008 - Night 2
